{"tid":2407860,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"房屋署問題 急問","createTime":"2021-02-14T11:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T01:38:59.000Z","uid":268327,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d181a30065f65fc0c42611913fbe2df4051d3f2c","tid":2407860,"uid":268327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:36:05.000Z","msg":"想請教一下<br />\n親戚屋企住緊2位老人家同個仔<br />\n兩位老人家先後離世<br />\n應該係2-4人單位。<br />\n有咩方法可以留返間屋？<br />\n<br />\n房署應該好快做野，<br />\n唔想連最後既回憶都抹殺埋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兒子50歲單身<br />\n如果年紀大啲應該唔會趕？<br />\n有冇得交換公屋之類？ 希望可以同兄弟姊妹家庭換咁？<br />\n因為間公屋唔買得，回憶太多。"},{"pid":"defa2dfff28b07d8283a09127068bdb540b3d216","tid":2407860,"uid":36673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"等搬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n70先可以唔先搬"},{"pid":"a3cb09886d492f2a175d666f80fe251d87c698b5","tid":2407860,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"defa2dfff28b07d8283a09127068bdb540b3d216","tid":2407860,"uid":36673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"等搬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n70先可以唔先搬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"唔係65<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71d843d432e8b6be6d2dbb9b57c8bf3be5ab875","tid":2407860,"uid":28076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"個單位本身幾大<br />\n如果細過35平方米既話2個人可以繼續住唔洗調"},{"pid":"2380596949aba072a3400bfd58092a9052c6aef0","tid":2407860,"uid":8520,"like":2,"d