score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"係咪租者置其屋範圍，係就可以買咗去。"},{"pid":"8e6fcf267839a877da3daea8cff40d014f8624b8","tid":2407860,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"冇喎，死左戶主？ <br />\n咁你親戚要出去租樓了，再重新排過公屋，入息審多次"},{"pid":"ac321fa943e44a9b3fbe9b875d717574573dd84c","tid":2407860,"uid":129169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T13:18:58.000Z","msg":"公屋戶主去世或遷出後，單位的租約可無條件地批予在單位內居住亦是認可成員的戶主配偶；倘若戶籍內並無戶主的在生配偶，有關的租約亦可批予在單位內居住的其他認可成員，但他們須接受「全面經濟狀況審查」（包括入息及資產審查）及「住宅物業權審查」，以釐定他們批出新租約的資格及應繳的租金水平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入息資產搞多次，過就搬，唔過就留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下你親戚係咪公屋富戶啦"},{"pid":"b0eb9b76db888c2f50f8d82f103608560e679609","tid":2407860,"uid":27716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"你親戚 姐係個仔 有冇落名先？<br />\n冇落名 已經乜都冇架啦啵"},{"pid":"740bdca5ed60e75beb42444647a1cb2910f0ef2f","tid":2407860,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76562f6640896d360e4f296b8d70151da9d0539c","tid":2407860,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3cb09886d492f2a175d666f80fe251d87c698b5","tid":2407860,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"defa2dfff28b07d8283a09127068bdb540b3d216","tid":2407860,"uid":36673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"等搬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n70先可以唔先搬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"唔係65<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T13:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vmaHE0j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvmaHE0j.png&h=bba4969d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n房屋署白紙黑字寫晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"ok 咁樓主安心調細房啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59e568db888f48cc94dababb5f1e7eb47db026b","tid":2407860,"uid":67465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"其實房署點知戶主同成員去世？"},{"pid":"4c4bd5db0b1e5cd1996cdded92c6d576e832b80e","tid":2407860,"uid":377234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T13:51:37.000Z","msg":"但唔係有$會俾返你咩，你去拎筆錢排居屋lo"},{"pid":"3d195748622c2ba0978683811248c503931ee5b5","tid":2407860,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f59e568db888f48cc94dababb5f1e7eb47db026b","tid":2407860,"uid":67465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"其實房署點知戶主同成員去世？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"一.如果仲有其他戶主，你要主動申報<br />\n二.如果全家都死曬，靠定期抽查同屋村主任造訪"},{"pid":"2887d2ec856dcef5f66140b2cbd61a5de7307665","tid":2407860,"uid":138127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d195748622c2ba0978683811248c503931ee5b5","tid":2407860,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f59e568db888f48cc94dababb5f1e7eb47db026b","tid":2407860,"uid":67465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"其實房署點知戶主同成員去世？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"一.如果仲有其他戶主，你要主動申報<br />\n二.如果全家都死曬，靠定期抽查同屋村主任造訪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}